# Content Generation Prompts

## Blog Post Prompt
"Write a high-quality blog post about [topic]. Use a professional tone, include an introduction, 3 main sections, and a conclusion."

## Improved Version
"Write a detailed blog post about [topic] for beginners. Include:
- Clear introduction
- 3 actionable sections
- Real-world examples
- Conclusion with key takeaways"

## Key Improvement
More structure = better output quality
